### ============================================================

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/v1

### ============================================================
### PUBLIC ROUTES (No Authentication Required)
### ============================================================

### Convert Image URL to Base64
# Used to bypass CORS when generating ticket images
# Query Params: ?url={imageUrl}
GET {{baseUrl}}/utils/image-to-base64?url=https://example.com/image.jpg

### Expected Response:
# {
#     "success": true,
#     "data": {
#         "base64": "data:image/jpeg;base64,/9j/4AAQSkZJRgABAQAAAQABAAD...",
#         "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
#         "size": 15240
#     }
# }

###

### Error Response (Invalid URL):
# {
#     "success": false,
#     "message": "Failed to fetch image from URL"
# }

###
